Add simple setup.py

Having a setup.py allows to easily get the .py files compiled into
.pyc, which is good because by default, Buildroot only keeps .pyc
files on the target.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Petazzoni <thomas.petazzoni@free-electrons.com>

